Foundation I Mudlib SimulEfun: unguarded()

mixed unguarded(function f);

DESCRIPTION
Calls function f based solely upon the privelidges
of the object making the call, bypassing the rest od the
stack.

EXAMPLE
unguarded((: file_exists, "/secure/daemon/master.c" :)) better return true

LOCATION
/secure/SimulEfun/security.c

SEE ALSO
query_privs()
